Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.63,0:07:17.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們會試試的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Well... we'll give it a try.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.06,0:07:19.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先生們  大家先坐下來\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Gentlemen, why don't we go have a sit down?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.25,0:07:20.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們談談下一步安排  好嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}We'll talk over the next steps. All right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.63,0:07:22.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這邊走\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Yeah. Right this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.10,0:07:31.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是想良心無愧嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}What do you want, a clean conscience?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.26,0:07:33.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算用塊牛肉來測試它  我也不在乎\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Test it with a slab of beef for all I care.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.73,0:07:36.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只希望不要背離了我們的設計初衷\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}What I want is to use it for what we originally designed it as.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.20,0:07:38.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用于震懾\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}A deterrent.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.86,0:07:41.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒人說過要用來微波加熱別人的肺\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Nobody said anything about microwaving people's lungs.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.46,0:07:42.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是戰爭\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}It's war.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.70,0:07:44.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我們賴以為生的產業\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}It's the business we're in.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.03,0:07:47.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你記得當初雇用我時說的套話嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Remember what you sold it to me as when you hired me?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.60,0:07:49.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,致力于防御\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Defense.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.80,0:07:51.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是有部分屬實的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}And that's still partially true.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.10,0:07:53.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但戰爭是樁好生意\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}But war is good business.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.06,0:07:55.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人口販賣也算\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}So is human trafficking.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.36,0:07:57.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬克  我們效力于國防高級研究計劃局\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}We work for DARPA, Mark.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.44,0:07:59.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,效力于政府\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}We work for the government.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.86,0:08:02.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,"我不知道第三次世界大戰會用什么武器\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}"I don't know what weapons we'll use to fight in World War III,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.33,0:08:04.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但第四次世界大戰會用..."\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}but World War IV will be fought with..."
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.35,0:08:06.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,"木棍和石塊"  愛因斯坦如是說\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}"Sticks and stones." said Albert Einstein.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.60,0:08:08.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-他也為政府工作  -沒錯\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- He worked for the government. - That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.36,0:08:10.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你去問他\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}And if you ask him, I don't think
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.98,0:08:12.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想他不會覺得那是他最輝煌的時刻\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}he thought that was his finest hour.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.80,0:08:15.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他肯定也會對把活人瞬間燒糊有意見的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I'm sure he has feelings about flash-boiling human flesh.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.10,0:08:18.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想過要研究有全感知反饋的義肢嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Ever think about prosthetic limbs with full sensory feedback?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.80,0:08:21.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,研究義肢無助于打勝仗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Prosthetics... don't win wars.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.93,0:08:23.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你聽到了嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Did you hear that?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.70,0:08:26.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是你逐漸失去的作為科學家的同情心\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}That is the empathetic scientist in you dying.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.13,0:08:30.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你和伙計們說了怎么操控射線了嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Did you brief your guys on how to operate the ray?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.96,0:08:32.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-說了  -很好\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- I did. - Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.33,0:08:33.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你可以開始收拾行李了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Then you can start packing.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.86,0:08:36.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能說具體點嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Can you be more specific?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.10,0:08:40.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是關于這些護目鏡的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}About these goggles here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.72,0:08:45.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的超光譜護目鏡已裝備給東歐\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Your... hyperspectral goggles being deployed by
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.25,0:08:48.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,摩爾多瓦戰役中的特種部隊\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}special forces in eastern Europe in the Moldovan war.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.83,0:08:50.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早知道了  我看了現場報告\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I'm aware. I read the field reports.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.52,0:08:52.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  你還沒看這份報告\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}No, you have not read this report.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.66,0:08:55.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奧倫德親自打電話給我  奧倫德將軍\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Orland called me personally. General Orland.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.86,0:08:59.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他說那邊的情況有點敏感\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}He said things are very... sensitive down there.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.30,0:09:04.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們見到了些東西\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}And they're... seeing things.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.83,0:09:06.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么東西\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Okay. Like what?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.20,0:09:09.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們不愿意告訴我\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}They won't tell me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.10,0:09:11.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們不愿意分享影像內容\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}They won't share the video feed.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.70,0:09:13.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不愿意討論所見之物\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}They won't discuss what they're seeing.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.73,0:09:15.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們只想讓首席工程師過去\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}They just want the lead engineer
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.18,0:09:16.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,提供建議和咨詢\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}down there to advise and consult.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.86,0:09:21.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你發明這些護目鏡是為了保護我們的人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Look, you invented these goggles to keep our guys safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.76,0:09:23.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而如今  他們需要你的幫助\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Well, now they need your help.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.90,0:09:25.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當作是為了防御吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Think of it as defense.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.80,0:09:43.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我來重啟制導系統\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Let me reboot the guidance system.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.60,0:09:45.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鎖得很死  我們要把它拉出來\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}It's locked tight. We have to pull it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.85,0:09:53.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\pos(35,179)}{\fn方正细黑一_GBK\fs12\b1\bord0\shad0\3c&H2F2F2F&\fad(400,0)\2a&HFF&}{\K70}摩爾多瓦  東歐\N\N\N\N\N\N{\K51}{\K60}美軍空軍基地
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.80,0:09:54.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  走吧  移走它\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}All right, let's go. Move it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.96,0:10:10.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-馬克·克萊恩  -什么\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- Mark Clyne? - What?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.96,0:10:12.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你設計的頭盔攝像機嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You the guy that designed the helmet cam?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.90,0:10:14.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  馬克·克萊恩\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Yes. Mark clyne.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.20,0:10:15.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是詹姆斯·奧倫德  跟我來\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}James Orland. Come with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.60,0:10:21.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這里又來了很多新士兵\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}A lot of new boots on the ground here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.26,0:10:22.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個國家一團糟\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}The country's in chaos.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.10,0:10:26.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叛軍主要是由軍事獨裁者余黨組成的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}The insurgency is mostly remnants of the military dictatorship
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.81,0:10:28.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直到兩個月前他們還控制著該地區\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}that ran this place until about two months ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.16,0:10:31.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,起初  在國家的北部地區\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}And their popular support
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.90,0:10:33.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,俄羅斯邊境附近\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}is primarily in the north part of the country,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.46,0:10:35.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和首都這里  他們都擁有廣泛支持\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}near the Russian border, and here in the capital.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.06,0:10:38.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,問題在于他們的軍隊都訓練有素\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}The problem is their forces are well-trained.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.80,0:10:41.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們威脅要把局勢發展成全面內戰\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}They're threatening to turn this whole thing into a civil war.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.13,0:10:50.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,俄羅斯曾統治摩爾多瓦  后又失去控制\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Moldova. Russians had it, lost it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.80,0:10:53.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,國家獨立了  但內部紛爭不斷\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}It became independent, but it's struggling internally.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.99,0:10:56.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一方面  是叛軍作亂\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}On the one hand, you have an insurgency,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.03,0:10:59.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全都是政府的前精銳部隊\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}made up of the regime's former elite soldiers.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.76,0:11:01.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們全都訓練有素且極度危險\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}They're well-trained and dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.80,0:11:03.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,另一方面  這里的大部分國民\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}On the other, you have most of the population,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.96,0:11:06.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都想推翻政府的統治\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}who are tearing down the regime's flags
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.20,0:11:07.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,渴望新政府\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}and demanding a new government.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.36,0:11:09.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管有多復雜\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Civil unrest, as complicated as it is,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.79,0:11:11.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,內亂是我們所熟悉的事情\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}is a business we're familiar with.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.03,0:11:13.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們覺得自己擅長處理內亂\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}We like to think we're good at it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.03,0:11:16.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是你的攝像機發現的這個...\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}But this thing your camera found...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.80,0:11:19.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是種全新的玩意兒\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}It's a whole new piece of business.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.83,0:11:28.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒法把這個視頻交給美軍歐洲司令部\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I can't send this video to EUCOM.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.35,0:11:30.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是擔心他們會認為這是個玩笑\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I'm just afraid they'd think it's a joke.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.30,0:11:31.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,國防部沒有幽默感\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}DOD doesn't have a sense of humor.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.00,0:11:34.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通常沒有  幫我們裝好\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Typically not. Hook us up.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.23,0:11:39.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我相信這些東西有科學的解釋\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I'm sure there's a scientific explanation for what's on these,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.03,0:11:41.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是在你告訴我之前\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}but until you tell me,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.10,0:11:43.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是不會把它上交指揮系統的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I'm not sending it up the chain of command.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.93,0:11:47.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-搞定了  -是的  長官\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- You done? - Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.20,0:11:49.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-出去把我們鎖好  在外面等著  -是\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- Get out. Seal us in. Wait outside. - Sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.26,0:11:57.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這里沒有人對這個有任何頭緒\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Nobody here has been able to make heads or tails of this.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.93,0:12:00.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由于一些我無法隨意告知你的原因\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}It's thrown a wrench into our entire operation
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.23,0:12:02.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們的整個行動都被攪亂了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}for reasons I'm not at liberty to discuss with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.00,0:12:06.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只能告訴你我們急需解釋\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I can tell you we need answers fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.96,0:12:32.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-介意我來嗎  -你這么快就看到了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- Do you mind? - You spotted that quick.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.66,0:12:36.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五個頭盔攝像機\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Five different helmet cams
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.90,0:12:39.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在過去三周內拍到了相似的東西\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}picked up something similar in the last three weeks.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.20,0:12:43.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最初情報技術人員\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}At first, our signals
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.17,0:12:45.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,認為那是干擾信號\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}intelligence tech wrote it off as interference.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.06,0:12:47.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那可不是干擾信號\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}That's not interference.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.36,0:12:50.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得要是干擾信號的話\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I don't think you'd fly me all the way here
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.94,0:12:52.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會讓我大老遠飛到這里來\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}for interference.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.36,0:12:55.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想跟我說說你的想法嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Wanna tell me what you're thinking?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.20,0:12:57.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想讓你先說出你的想法\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I want you to tell me what you're thinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.00,0:13:00.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我...暫時沒什么想法\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I don't know what I'm thinking... yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.96,0:13:02.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但這總是有解釋的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}But there is an explanation.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.06,0:13:08.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是第一次觀測到的畫面  另外三次類似\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}That was the first sighting. Three others just like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.80,0:13:10.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最后一次有些不同\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}The last was different.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.18,0:13:12.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為牽扯到一位三角洲部隊成員\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}It involved a member of Delta Force,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.20,0:13:13.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這讓事情變得極其敏感\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}that makes it particularly sensitive.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.73,0:13:16.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這位是中情局的弗蘭·麥迪遜\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}This is Fran Madison with CIA.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.76,0:13:19.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這里的特別行動都是中情局的秘密任務\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}What special ops does here is done under CIA covert operations.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.76,0:13:22.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在我們繼續之前你得把這個簽了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You need to sign this before we go any further.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.66,0:13:25.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-這是什么  -敏感信息保證書\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- What is this? - It's an SCI oath.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.60,0:13:27.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你泄露了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You're acknowledging it's life
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.09,0:13:29.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告訴你的任何事  你將被判終身監禁\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}in prison if you reveal anything you're told.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.22,0:13:47.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\pos(317,232)}{\fn方正细黑一_GBK\fs11\bord0\shad0\3c&H2F2F2F&\fad(0,350)\2a&HFF&\b0}{\K30}敏感信息隔離設施
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.33,0:14:07.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-找到戴維斯的文件  -是  長官\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- Cue up the Davis file, please. - Yes, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.16,0:14:10.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三天前我們中城區進行了一次突擊行動\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Three days ago we conducted a raid in mid-city.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.70,0:14:13.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們的通訊時斷時續\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Our communications were intermittent,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.39,0:14:15.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有一位隊員與隊伍失聯了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}and a guy got separated from the group...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.30,0:14:18.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最終他在行動中被殺\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Where he ended up killed in action.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.63,0:14:22.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他比任何人離得都近\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}He got closer than anybody.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.10,0:14:24.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太近了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Too close.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.10,0:14:45.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這里是D組1隊  你們看到了嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Dagger team 1, you seeing this?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.68,0:14:47.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這里有東西在干擾信號\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}There's some kind of disturbance here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.23,0:14:51.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戴維斯  什么東西  你看到什么了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Davis, what is that? What are you seeing?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.93,0:14:53.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,見鬼\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}What the hell?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.70,0:15:05.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克里斯·戴維斯中士\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Sergeant Chris Davis.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.80,0:15:09.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,經歷過三次戰爭的老兵  精英中的精英\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Three-tour combat vet. Best of the best.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.86,0:15:19.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近幾周我們在全城范圍內都發現了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}In the last few weeks we've been finding bodies around the city
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.86,0:15:21.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死法相同的尸體\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}that were killed in the same way.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.20,0:15:24.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尸檢無法得出結論\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}The autopsies defied all explanation.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.76,0:15:26.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們的內臟被冰凍住\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Their internal organs were frozen
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.80,0:15:29.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然而皮膚卻被燒灼和腐蝕了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}and yet, their skin was burned and corroded.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.26,0:15:32.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從摩爾多瓦友軍方面\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}The only response from the allied
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.10,0:15:34.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得到的唯一回應  只有震驚和困惑\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Moldovan military contact is shock, confusion.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.93,0:15:35.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有憤怒\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}And there's anger.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.76,0:15:37.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有一些少年\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}There's teenagers
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.70,0:15:40.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在出事地點噴涂"滅絕幽魂"的記號\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}spray-painting "Genocide Aratare" at kill sites.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.60,0:15:41.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-滅絕什么  -"幽魂"\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- Genocide...? - "Aratare."
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.80,0:15:44.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當地的傳說  戰爭的鬼魂\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}It's a local myth. The ghosts of war.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.80,0:15:48.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,"如同噩夢一般"  大概是這個意思\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}"As nightmarish as." That's the literal translation.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.80,0:15:51.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-還很有詩意  -那是他們的迷信\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- That's very poetic. - Well, they're superstitious.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.23,0:15:53.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們不知怎地認為...\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}They somehow think...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.23,0:15:57.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戰爭的恐怖喚醒了一些非自然的力量\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}the horrors of the war have kicked up something unnatural.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.73,0:16:01.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-我們希望你能給出別的理論  -你怎么看\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- We hope you have an alternate theory. - What do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.66,0:16:04.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我認為你們得給它們起個新名字\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Think you need a new name for them.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.39,0:16:04.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除了這個\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Beyond that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.83,0:16:08.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我一份這些數據的拷貝  給我點時間\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Give me a copy of the data, some time...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.29,0:16:08.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}That's not possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.86,0:16:10.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們想讓我現在就搞清楚\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You want me to figure this out right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.86,0:16:13.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-我們需要你的看法  -我還沒什么看法\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- We want your assessment. - I don't have one yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.13,0:16:15.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  我們就得把目前的理論\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Then, I think we have to send our working theory
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.49,0:16:16.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上交給指揮系統\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}up the chain of command.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.66,0:16:17.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不想這樣做\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I don't wanna do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.71,0:16:19.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧  目前的理論是什么\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Okay. What is your working theory?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.80,0:16:22.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們認為這是一種隱身技術\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}The agency thinks this is some kind of cloaking technology.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.00,0:16:26.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叛軍士兵穿著動態偽裝服\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Insurgent soldiers wearing active camouflage.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.30,0:16:28.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這個國家嗎  那么先進的技術\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}In this country? Something that advanced?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.30,0:16:29.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中情局知道歐洲和亞洲的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}CIA knows a few groups in Europe
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.71,0:16:31.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一些組織可能在研究動態偽裝服\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}and Asia could be working on active camouflage.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.26,0:16:34.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,國防部高級研究計劃局也在研究隱形技術\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}DARPA's worked on cloaking technology.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.23,0:16:36.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們離原型都還差好多年\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}We're years away from a prototype.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.06,0:16:37.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也許有人領先了你們\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Maybe somebody beat you to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.62,0:16:39.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們已經是這個領域最先進的了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}DARPA is the leader in the field.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.60,0:16:40.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你確定嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Are you certain of that?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.23,0:16:43.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地方政府斥巨資進行武器研究\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}The regime spent heavily on weapons research.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.86,0:16:45.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,腐敗  松散的法治\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Corruption, loose legislation.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.30,0:16:47.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對一個想要低調的軍事實驗室來說\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You're a military lab and want obscurity?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.33,0:16:49.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-這里是悄悄進行研究的完美地點  -好吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- This is a great place to work and hide. - Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.73,0:16:56.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們假設這是一種隱身技術\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Let's say it is cloaking technology.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.83,0:16:59.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么解釋死因\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}How do you account for cause of death?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.69,0:17:01.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對受害者的沖擊波\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}A shock delivered to the victim.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.10,0:17:03.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得你只是瞎猜的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I think you're reaching.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.36,0:17:05.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們的工作需要進行推測\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Our business requires us to make suppositions.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.73,0:17:07.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而我的工作需要去證實這些推測\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}My business requires us to prove them.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.80,0:17:10.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們的技術人員的工作是找到故障\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Your technician's job is to find glitches,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.90,0:17:11.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以他們看到了故障\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}so, he sees glitches.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.76,0:17:14.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們的工作是找到敵人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Your job is to find the enemy,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.21,0:17:15.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以你們看到了敵人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}so, you see the enemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.23,0:17:18.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本地人相信鬼魂  他們就看到了鬼魂\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Locals believe in spirits, so they see spirits.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.63,0:17:21.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在某一方面  每個人都有自己的偏見\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Everyone is biased, in one way or another.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.13,0:17:23.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以  現在我的回答是\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}So, my answer to you right
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.39,0:17:25.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們目前缺少數據來支持任何理論\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}now is that we lack data to support any theory.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.26,0:17:27.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.60,0:17:31.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你需要什么來得出更肯定的結論\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}What do you need to make a more definitive statement?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.96,0:17:42.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首先  你們得有更好的畫面\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}First, you need a better shot.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.36,0:17:44.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這正是我想要的  更好的畫面\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}That's what I'm looking for, a better shot.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.23,0:17:46.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么做\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}How?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.96,0:17:49.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-這邊  長官  -就是這個\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- Right here, sir. - That's it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.70,0:17:55.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我從DARPA帶來了這個  超光譜攝像機\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I brought this from DARPA. A hyperspectral camera.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.30,0:17:58.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比你們用的頭盔攝像機更強大的設備\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}A more powerful version of the helmet cams your guys are using.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.33,0:18:00.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它能看到深層次的光譜\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}It sees deeper into the spectrum of light.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.60,0:18:02.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管是否可見  只要有東西\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Visible or invisible, if something's there,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.74,0:18:03.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它就能觀察到\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}this'll pick it up.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.13,0:18:07.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你能把這東西安在三角洲部隊的戰車上嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Can you mount this thing... on a delta vehicle?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.33,0:18:09.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-當然可以  -很好\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- I don't see why not. - All right, good.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.36,0:18:11.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們每天在城里都有行動\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}We run missions into the city every day.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.76,0:18:14.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我把戰地技術人員找來  你教他怎么操作\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I'll put you with our field tech, tell him how to operate it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.70,0:18:17.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不想讓我之外的第二個人來操作這部攝像機\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I wouldn't put a tech in between this camera and myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.86,0:18:22.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你想親自操作\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}So, you wanna operate it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.86,0:18:24.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要想拍到關鍵畫面...\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}If you want that kill shot...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.37,0:18:26.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,需要快速的臨場反應\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}you'll need a fast reaction time out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.93,0:18:28.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次行動  你跟三角洲部隊一起\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Next mission, you ride with delta.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.30,0:18:31.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們會帶你接近那東西\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}They're gonna get you close to this thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.61,0:18:33.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等你給我搞到關鍵畫面\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You get me the kill shot...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.96,0:18:36.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就可以直接拎包回弗吉尼亞\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}you can go home to Virginia without unpacking.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.60,0:18:41.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有個轉子壞了  你得把它換掉\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Got a bad rotor, you gotta swap that out.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.20,0:18:44.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把它焊在前面板上\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Weld it onto the front panel.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.13,0:18:54.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞧瞧這個\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Well, well, well. Toll, check that out.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.26,0:18:57.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-這家伙在做什么  -我不知道\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- What's this guy up to, man? - I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.26,0:18:58.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你相信這家伙嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Believe this guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.66,0:19:00.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-如果有作用的話  -說真的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- If it works. - For real.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.03,0:19:05.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽說你要在我們的車上裝個攝像機\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Heard you're installing a camera on our truck.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.20,0:19:07.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是你不把50口徑機槍拆下來我本來沒意見\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Which was fine until you ripped out that 50 Cal.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.66,0:19:09.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你拆了把槍換了部攝像機上去\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You're taking down a gun to put up a camera?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.13,0:19:12.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有那里有空間放置攝像機\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}It's the only place large enough to mount it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.16,0:19:16.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們能明白吧  我知道這聽起來像個壞主意\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You guys get that, right? I know it sounds like a terrible idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.83,0:19:19.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們更喜歡跟帶我們的人合作\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}We prefer to dance with who brung us...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.11,0:19:20.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克萊恩博士  懂了嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Dr. Clyne. You get that, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.00,0:19:23.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,"跟帶你們的人合作"  我并不懂\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}"Dance with who brung you"? No, actually, I don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.16,0:19:28.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這輛車救過我們的命很多次\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}This truck has saved our lives, many times.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.86,0:19:29.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.30,0:19:32.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們知道這輛車是克萊恩博士的團隊制造的嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You guys know Dr. Clyne's team built that truck?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.13,0:19:35.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克萊恩博士在DARPA工作\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Clyne works over at DARPA.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.26,0:19:39.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我跟他的團隊緊密合作過\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I've worked closely with his group.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.17,0:19:41.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去過他們在弗吉尼亞的設施\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Been to their facilities in Virginia.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.73,0:19:43.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很高興見到你  克萊恩博士\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Good to see you, Dr. Clyne.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.41,0:19:44.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是  卡布瑞拉上尉\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Good to see you, Captain Cabrera.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.73,0:19:47.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們給這些車改裝了更堅固輕便的裝甲\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}They retrofitted these trucks with tougher, lighter weight armor.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.03,0:19:50.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們設計了裝載機來搬運重物\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}They designed the mechanical loaders that do the heavy lifting,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.03,0:19:53.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給你們省了力氣\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}so you boys don't strain yourselves too hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.86,0:19:55.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事實上  克萊恩博士本人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Matter of fact, Dr. Clyne himself
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.80,0:19:58.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還設計了輕薄的凱夫拉連體緊身衣\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}developed the thin weight Kevlar body stocking that literally...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.93,0:20:00.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來保護你們的蛋蛋\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}protects your balls.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.90,0:20:03.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我希望你們\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}So, I would think there'd be
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.39,0:20:06.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都能對克萊恩博士心存感激\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}nothing but goodwill in this group for Dr. Clyne.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.33,0:20:11.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-塞申斯少校  -上尉  讓你的人退下\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- Major Sessions. - Captain, have your men fall back.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.23,0:20:14.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-都散開  -把它放下\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- Get back to it. - Get it done.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.63,0:20:15.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少校  這位是克萊恩博士\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Major, this is Dr. Clyne.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.60,0:20:18.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在過去五年他和我們合作過多次\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}He's worked with us eight or ten times over the last five years.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.16,0:20:21.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要和突擊隊一起去擊殺鬼影嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You go out with the assault team on hunting ghost?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.06,0:20:23.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  長官\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}No, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.73,0:20:24.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是個好人  少校\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}He's a good man, major.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.83,0:20:28.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好  但我不喜歡帶游客執行作戰任務\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}That's great. I'm just not a fan of taking tourists on combat missions.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.36,0:20:29.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,長官  我不是游客\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Sir, I'm not a tourist.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.93,0:20:32.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果沒攜帶突擊步槍  那你就是個游客\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}If you're not carrying an M4, you're a tourist.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.30,0:20:33.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你堅持  我可以配槍\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I can carry one, if you'd like.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.86,0:20:35.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少校  我們得把克萊恩博士帶去戰場\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Major, we gotta get Dr. Clyne out in the field
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.66,0:20:37.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣他才能追蹤目標  幫助我們擊斃它\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}so he can track the target force and get us a kill shot.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.96,0:20:40.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個儀器需要多久才能運轉\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}How long before this equipment's operational?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.36,0:20:41.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幾個小時吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}A few hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.73,0:20:43.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-會有用嗎  -如果我們離得夠近\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- Is it gonna work? - If we get close enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.90,0:20:48.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戴維斯中士...就離得夠近了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Let me tell you something. Sergeant Davis...he got close enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.06,0:20:51.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是我們最頂尖的三角洲隊員\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}That's the best delta that we had.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.23,0:20:56.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最好保證你的儀器也是最頂尖的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Make sure your equipment is top-notch this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.36,0:21:06.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-他們情同手足  -我理解\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- They were like brothers. - I get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.90,0:21:08.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.16,0:21:13.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚上好  博士\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Evening, doc.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.96,0:21:29.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽說你倆一見如故\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Hear you two hit it off bigtime.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.26,0:21:37.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-她可以放松一點  -你也是\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- She can come off a bit intense. - Yeah. So can you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.83,0:21:39.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我來這兒只是幫你們找到這東西\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I'm just here to find this thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.70,0:21:41.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了找到它  你都愿意參與作戰任務\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You're willing to go on a combat mission to find it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.66,0:21:45.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她也是\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}She is, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.10,0:21:49.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,華盛頓給她施加了太大的壓力\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}She's under a lot of pressure from D.C.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.23,0:21:51.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們想要答案  而她負責找出答案\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}They want an answer and it's her job to give them one.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.96,0:21:53.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在任務名單上看到了你們的名字\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Saw your names on a mission roster.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.63,0:21:56.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道這是最緊要的事\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I knew this was a top priority...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.33,0:22:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但他們把你們倆都派來...\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}but for them to embed you both...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.23,0:22:05.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用擔心我\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Well, you don't have to worry about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.76,0:22:08.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不擔心你  博士  我擔心這東西\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I'm not worried about you, doc. I'm worried about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.93,0:22:13.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她認為這是一種隱形技術\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}She's hoping it's cloaking technology.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.73,0:22:15.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你覺得呢\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}What do you think it is?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.83,0:22:19.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們都還沒想到的某種東西\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Something no one's thought of yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.33,0:22:26.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位  昨天18點\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Gentlemen, yesterday at 1800 hours,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.60,0:22:29.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,U組去杜勒斯地執行偵察任務時\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Utah team left here on a recon mission to Durlesti,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.60,0:22:31.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,與叛軍交火了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}when they were engaged by insurgents.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.26,0:22:34.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們設法弄清交火時他們說了什么\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}We managed to hear most of their chatter during the firefight,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.30,0:22:35.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但結果并不理想\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}but comes were unreliable.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.16,0:22:38.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目標是這里的一棟五層建筑\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Target is a five-story apartment building here.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.83,0:22:43.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們認為活著的U組隊員被關押在四樓\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}We think what's left of utah team is being held on the fourth floor,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.20,0:22:44.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,位于西北角的房間里\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}in the northwest corner apartment.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.93,0:22:47.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們將深入叛軍占領區域\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}We're gonna be knee-deep in an insurgent-held area in the city.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.96,0:22:49.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以  做好交戰準備\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}So, we should expect a fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.13,0:22:51.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最后一件事\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}One last thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.83,0:22:54.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們的人被抓住之前\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Before our guys were grabbed,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.07,0:22:55.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通過無線電匯報了看到的東西\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}they radioed in that they saw
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.66,0:22:57.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們稱之為  超光譜異形物\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}what we're now calling hyperspectral anomalies.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.23,0:23:00.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,此次任務要速戰速決\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Your mission is a quick extraction.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.01,0:23:01.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到U組隊員  帶他們出來\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You get our guys and you get out.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.20,0:23:06.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果交火  將異形物就地消滅\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}However, if engaged, neutralize the anomalies in the area.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.23,0:23:07.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,消滅他們\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Neutralize them?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.73,0:23:12.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-怎么消滅  -我們要對付的是什么\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- How? - Yeah, what are we dealing with here?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.26,0:23:15.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們認為是穿著先進電子偽裝服的敵方士兵\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}We believe these are enemy soldiers in advanced electronic camouflage.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.90,0:23:17.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以  交火時務必小心  如果他們...\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}So, be surgical when you fire. If they are...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.19,0:23:18.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果不清楚他們是什么  也許我們該...\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}If we don't really know what they are, maybe we should...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.23,0:23:21.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思  你想補充什么嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Excuse me? Would you like to add something?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.00,0:23:25.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果他們穿戴了隱形技術\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}If they are wearing cloaking technology,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.93,0:23:28.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們要盡可能將其完好無損地帶回來\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}you need to bring it back as intact as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.80,0:23:31.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克萊恩博士和麥迪遜特工會和你們一起去\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Dr. Clyne and Agent Madison will be on mission with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.13,0:23:34.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克萊恩博士會在車隊中第二輛反伏擊車上\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Dr. Clyne will be monitoring your helmet-cam feeds
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.83,0:23:36.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,監測你們頭盔攝像機的反饋影像\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}from the second MRAP vehicle in the convoy.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.80,0:23:40.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塞申斯少校會帶領D組1隊進行營救\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Major Sessions will lead dagger team 1 to do the extraction.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.06,0:23:43.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿好裝備  隨時待命\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Stay on come. Get your gear.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.76,0:23:47.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧  伙計\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Partner, let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.82,0:23:49.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,AJ  檢查前部和中部\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}AJ, front and center.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.86,0:23:51.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,檢查武器  比利\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Weapons check, Billy.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.80,0:23:53.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒問題\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.30,0:24:30.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這路對你來說不夠平坦嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Our ride not smooth enough for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.23,0:24:32.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還敢說自己很厲害{\fs14}[屁股堅硬]{\fs}\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}And you call yourself hard-ass.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.06,0:24:34.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們真應該重新鋪一下這條路  兄弟\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}They really need to repave these roads, man.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:00.73,0:25:03.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  伙計們  我們正在進入廢棄區\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}All right, guys, we're coming into the abandoned zone.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:03.30,0:25:05.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做好面對大批叛軍的準備吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Expect a heavy insurgent presence.
