Dialogue: 0,0:37:12.58,0:37:14.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克萊恩  別管攝像機了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Clyne, leave the camera.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:15.66,0:37:17.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快走  克萊恩\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Come on, clyne.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:24.96,0:37:25.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快快快\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Go, go, go.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:29.70,0:37:30.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快走\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Move, move.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:36.20,0:37:37.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,掩護\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Cover.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:38.03,0:37:39.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-快走  -快起來\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- Let's go. - Get up, get up.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:40.13,0:37:41.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:41.16,0:37:42.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走走走\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Go, go, go.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:44.06,0:37:45.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你去哪了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Where you been?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:46.76,0:37:47.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安全\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Clear.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:48.36,0:37:49.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰受傷了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Who's injured?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:49.83,0:37:51.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-迪亞茲  -我腳踝好像受傷了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- Diaz? - I think my ankle's broke.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:53.06,0:37:55.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們需要空運  但我聯系不上基地\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}We need an airlift. I can't get a signal to base.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:55.54,0:37:56.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,繼續嘗試\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Keep trying.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:56.16,0:37:57.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通訊設備給我\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Com.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:01.26,0:38:03.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呼叫基地  呼叫基地\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Archer Lima 2. Archer Lima 2.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:04.20,0:38:06.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這里是D組1隊  收到請回答\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}This is Dagger team 1, over.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:07.00,0:38:08.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒事\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I'm good. I'm good.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:09.16,0:38:10.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它們能從那里進來嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Can they get in that way?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:12.93,0:38:13.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你沒事吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:14.00,0:38:16.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呼叫基地  這里是D組1隊\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Archer Lima 2, this is Dagger team 1.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:16.06,0:38:17.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,收到請回答\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Do you copy? Over.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:20.23,0:38:23.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呼叫基地  這里是D組1隊  收到請回答\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Archer Lima 2, this is Dagger team 1. Do you copy? Over.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:28.70,0:38:31.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么樣  你在流血\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}How you doing? You're bleeding.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:36.26,0:38:37.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:38.30,0:38:39.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你撞到頭了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You hit your head.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:40.70,0:38:41.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你撞到頭了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You hit your head.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:44.36,0:38:45.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你暈過去了嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Did you black out?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:47.86,0:38:48.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像是的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Yeah, I guess so.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:50.93,0:38:51.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少校\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Major.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:55.36,0:38:57.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-她的頭撞得挺嚴重的  -我看看\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- She hit her head pretty bad. - Let me see.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:59.73,0:39:00.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞳孔很大\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Pupils are huge.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:00.70,0:39:02.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,長官  我一直在發信號但他們收不到\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Sir, I'm sending but they're not receiving.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:02.73,0:39:05.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我發完后能聽到滴答聲  但是沒有應答\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I'm hearing a click back as soon as I sign over, but no answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:05.73,0:39:06.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,繼續嘗試\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Keep trying.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:06.66,0:39:08.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她嚇得不輕  照看好她\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}She's in shock. Keep an eye on her.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:09.00,0:39:11.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呼叫基地  這里是D組1隊  收到請回答\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Archer Lima 2, this is Dagger team 1. Do you copy? Over.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:11.80,0:39:12.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...去那邊\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}... over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:14.80,0:39:16.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其他人呢  U組其他人在哪\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Where's everyone else? Where's the rest of Utah?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:17.93,0:39:20.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是陳中士  我是U組的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I'm Sergeant Chen. I was with Utah.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:21.33,0:39:25.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們是昨晚第二個來的小組  來了八個\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}We were the second team in last night. There was eight of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:28.23,0:39:30.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們能確認U組誰已經陣亡了嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Do you have confirmed KIAs for Utah?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:30.16,0:39:31.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只能告訴你\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Well, I can tell you this much.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:32.36,0:39:35.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,科姆斯托克中士今年收不到圣誕賀卡了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Sergeant Comstock's not gonna be on your team Christmas card this year.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:35.83,0:39:38.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-你看到叛軍殺了科姆斯托克  -叛軍\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- You saw insurgents kill Comstock? - Insurgents?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:38.63,0:39:39.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他沒毛病吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Is this guy for real?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:41.63,0:39:44.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-你在哪躲著呢  -我是通訊兵\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- What rock were you under? - I was the radio operator.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:44.36,0:39:47.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們失去聯系了  我整晚都被困在卡車里\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}We lost com. I was stuck in the truck the whole night.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:47.10,0:39:49.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-我沒見到動態偽裝兵  -動態偽裝兵\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- I never saw the active camouflage. - Active camouflage?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:49.90,0:39:52.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根本就沒有這樣的士兵  就算有\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Even if there was a such thing, and there's not...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:53.90,0:39:56.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人類怎么可能穿著動態偽裝服穿過墻壁呢\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}How does a human wearing active camouflage walk through walls?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:56.83,0:39:59.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或被三個彈夾的穿甲彈打穿都沒死\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Or through three mags of armor-piercing ammo?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:59.33,0:40:01.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看到帕特對其中一個打了至少150發\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I saw Pat pump 150 rounds at one of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:03.10,0:40:05.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這東西至少殺了19個我們的人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}This thing's killed at least 19 of our men.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:06.76,0:40:08.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而我們還不知道它是什么東西\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}And we have no idea what it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:14.76,0:40:15.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克萊恩\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Clyne.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:18.60,0:40:19.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你見過它\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You saw it.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:20.73,0:40:21.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它是什么東西\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}What was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:23.23,0:40:24.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是人類\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Human.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:26.90,0:40:27.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有著人類的外形\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Had a human form.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:29.70,0:40:31.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它看著我  有自己的意識\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}It looked at me, it was conscious.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:35.23,0:40:36.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像個活人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Like a person.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:41.33,0:40:43.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么能解釋你看到的東西嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Is there anything that explains what you saw?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:45.03,0:40:46.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:48.20,0:40:51.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們把能用的護目鏡收集起來\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Let's pull together all the functional goggles that we have.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:51.23,0:40:53.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的護目鏡在撞擊中壞了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}My goggles were wasted in the crash, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:53.15,0:40:55.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的也是  撞壞了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Yeah. Mine, too. They're trashed.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:55.23,0:40:57.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別管護目鏡了  反正我們也沒辦法充電\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Forget the goggles. We can't recharge them anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:58.33,0:40:59.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我們怎么辦\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}So, what do we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:00.36,0:41:01.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們怎么發現它們\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}How are we supposed to see them?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:02.20,0:41:03.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也許那臺攝像機還能幫上忙\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Maybe that camera can still help us.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:06.60,0:41:08.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果能占領制高點\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}If we get to an elevated position,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:08.19,0:41:09.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,情況可能對我們更有利\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}we'd have a better vantage point.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:09.80,0:41:10.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來搭把手\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Help me with this?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:12.30,0:41:14.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們走  行動起來\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Let's go. Let's move out. Move.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:43.30,0:41:44.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到處都是\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}They're everywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:46.30,0:41:48.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么東西阻擋住了它們\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Something's stopping them.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:58.03,0:41:59.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,某種黑色沙土\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Some sort of black sand.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:00.90,0:42:02.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在那沙里摔了一跤\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I fell in that sand.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:03.16,0:42:05.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-我把它從手里摳出來了  -讓我看看\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- I had to... pick it out of my hand. - Let me see it.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:09.83,0:42:12.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-一小片尖銳金屬  -是鐵屑\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- Little, sharp pieces of metal. - They're iron filings.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:13.93,0:42:15.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-純鐵  -是啊\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- It's pure iron. - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:16.10,0:42:19.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一整條鐵屑  圍繞房子一圈\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}And there's a trail of it... All the way around the building.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:26.26,0:42:28.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是一道屏障  有人把它放在那的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}It's a barrier. Someone put it there.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:31.66,0:42:32.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來這里還有人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I don't think we're alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:33.60,0:42:35.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,整理好裝備  我們清理樓上\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Let's stack up and sweep upstairs.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:39.80,0:42:40.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞄準就開槍\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Point and shoot?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:41.63,0:42:42.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞄準就開槍\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Point and shoot.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:52.33,0:43:53.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突進  突進\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Breach! Breach!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:03.73,0:44:05.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-發現兒童  -安全\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- I've got kids. - Clear.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:05.76,0:44:07.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-安全  -解除警報\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- Clear. - All clear.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:08.70,0:44:10.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,派人守住長墻那里\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Tell them to take the long wall.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:19.03,0:44:21.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,問他們槍從哪來的  這里還有誰\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Ask them where they got this, and who else is here.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:27.13,0:44:28.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,問問他們工廠里\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Ask them if there's anyone
Dialogue: 0,0:44:28.49,0:44:30.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是否還有其他人  以及他們是否有槍\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}else in the factory, and do they have guns.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:43.23,0:44:45.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她說只有她們倆在這里\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}She says they're here alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:45.93,0:44:48.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就那一把槍  沒有士兵\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Only that one gun. No soldiers are here.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:49.20,0:44:51.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-一個人都沒有  -塞申斯少校\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- No one at all. - Major sessions.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:56.90,0:44:57.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出什么問題了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}What's the problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:57.93,0:44:59.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這工廠有自己的信號塔\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}This factory has its own transmission tower.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:59.93,0:45:01.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能發出很強的信號\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}It puts out a huge signal.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:02.00,0:45:03.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么問題嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}So, what's the problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:03.66,0:45:04.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,32公里內的所有人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Everyone within 20 miles
Dialogue: 0,0:45:04.60,0:45:06.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都能聽見我們和基地的通話\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}will hear our conversation with base.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:07.06,0:45:09.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,任何叛軍的電臺都能截獲我們的信號\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Any insurgent radio will pick up our transmission.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:10.76,0:45:13.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在最不用擔心的就是叛軍\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Insurgents are the least of your worries.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:13.76,0:45:15.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,盡快和奧倫德將軍取得聯系\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Connect me to General Orland as soon as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:18.70,0:45:20.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呼叫基地  這里是D組\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Archer Lima 2, Archer Lima 2, this is Dagger team.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:20.50,0:45:21.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能收到嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Do you copy?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:25.96,0:45:28.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呼叫基地  這里是D組\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Archer Lima 2, Archer Lima 2, this is dagger team.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:28.20,0:45:28.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能收到嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Do you copy?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:32.90,0:45:35.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呼叫基地  這里是D組\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Archer Lima 2, Archer Lima 2, this is dagger team.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:35.50,0:45:36.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能收到嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Do you copy?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:50.70,0:45:52.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們是我們的新兵\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You guys are our new recruits.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:53.16,0:45:55.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相信我  你們能幫上大忙\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}And believe me... we could use the help.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:05.20,0:46:07.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來吧  小鐵漢  看看你有什么本事\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Come on, tough guy. Show me what you got.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:10.93,0:46:12.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我得問你些事兒\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Hey, I need to ask you something.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:13.36,0:46:17.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,外面的屏障  是你的主意嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Was it your idea... to put the barrier... outside?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:20.70,0:46:23.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是他們父親  他們父親知道\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Their father. Their father knew.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:23.70,0:46:27.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們父親沿著建筑外圍\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Their father rolled open barrels of the iron shavings
Dialogue: 0,0:46:27.40,0:46:28.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,撒了幾桶鐵屑\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}around the building.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:29.23,0:46:30.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他救了他們的命\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}He saved their lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:32.96,0:46:34.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你父親呢\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}What happened to your father?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:35.96,0:46:38.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是個小拳擊手是吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You're a little scrapper, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:42.23,0:46:44.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伙計  你沒事吧  繼續  站起來\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Hey, buddy, you all right? Come on, get up.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:47.20,0:46:48.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在做什么\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:00.86,0:47:01.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是鬼魂嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Are you a ghost?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:03.06,0:47:04.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幽魂\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Aratare.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:06.13,0:47:07.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他說別說那個詞\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}He says, "Don't say that word."
Dialogue: 0,0:47:07.21,0:47:08.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,問他那些東西是什么\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Ask him what they are.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:11.16,0:47:12.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失落的靈魂\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Lost souls.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:13.06,0:47:14.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死者的靈魂\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Souls of the dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:16.30,0:47:18.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被困在生與死之間\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}They're trapped between life and death,
Dialogue: 0,0:47:18.66,0:47:20.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無法安息\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}and they can't find peace.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:22.13,0:47:23.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什么會這樣\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}How's that happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:26.83,0:47:27.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他說是因為戰爭\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}He says, "War."
Dialogue: 0,0:47:37.30,0:47:38.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,過來\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:42.96,0:47:44.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是他們的父親撒下了那些鐵屑\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}If their father was the one who put down the iron shavings,
Dialogue: 0,0:47:45.00,0:47:47.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那他比我們任何人都更了解那些東西\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}he knows more about these things than any of us do.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:48.23,0:47:49.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,問問她父親在哪兒\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Ask her where her father is.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:24.30,0:48:26.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她弟弟波格丹還不知道\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Her brother, Bogdan, doesn't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:27.00,0:48:28.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他以為父親只是出去求助了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}He thinks he went to get help.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:30.90,0:48:33.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是在外面弄屏障的時候死的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}He died outside, when he was making the barrier.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:34.16,0:48:35.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她只能把他帶回這里\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}She had to bring him in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:36.66,0:48:37.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很遺憾\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I'm so sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:40.80,0:48:42.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-我可以嗎  -嗯\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- Okay? - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:49.86,0:48:51.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,陶瓷片\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Ceramic tile.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:53.36,0:48:54.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,問問她父親是怎么知道\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Ask her how her father knew
Dialogue: 0,0:48:54.69,0:48:56.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鐵屑能阻擋幽魂的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}about the iron filings stopping the Aratare.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:57.63,0:48:59.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他還知道些什么\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}What else did he know about them?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:59.60,0:49:00.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她什么都不知道\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}She doesn't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:05.90,0:49:06.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬薩羅維\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}"Masarov."
Dialogue: 0,0:49:08.00,0:49:09.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-馬薩羅維是什么  -是一個地名\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- What is Masarov? - It's a place.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:09.96,0:49:11.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上游的一個區域\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}It's a district up the river.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:14.10,0:49:15.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這一切的源頭\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}It's where it all began.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:18.23,0:49:20.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幽魂殺人就是從那里開始的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}It's where the Aratare killings started.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:21.26,0:49:22.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幽魂\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Aratare.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:25.20,0:49:27.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要我說就把直升機停這兒\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I'm saying we land the helos right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:27.20,0:49:29.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們從這個屋頂撤離  趕緊離開這里\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Extract us from this roof and get us the hell out of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:30.00,0:49:32.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這里到處都是電話線和電力線\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}There are phone lines and power lines everywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:32.20,0:49:33.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直升機得飛得又低又慢\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}The helos would have to fly low and slow.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:33.83,0:49:35.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一個小孩都能扛著火箭筒把它打下來\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Easy pickings for a teenager with a shoulder rocket.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:36.63,0:49:37.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少校  現在是什么情況\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Major, can you get me up to speed?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:37.75,0:49:38.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和基地聯系過了嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You spoke with base?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:38.83,0:49:41.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聯系過了  將軍會派直升機來接我們\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Yeah. The General's sending in helos to come get us,
Dialogue: 0,0:49:41.75,0:49:45.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以及坦克來確保降落廣場周邊安全\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}and tanks to secure the landing zone in an open plaza
Dialogue: 0,0:49:45.60,0:49:47.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,距這里約八百米  黎明到達\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}about half a mile from here, at dawn.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:47.70,0:49:49.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,步行的話會很遠\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}That's a long way on foot.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:50.20,0:49:52.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你覺得我們能帶著小孩撐過八百米嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You think we can make it a half mile? With kids?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:52.96,0:49:54.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們別無選擇\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}We don't have an option. Okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:54.34,0:49:56.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所有的路要么被封死要么埋了地雷\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}All the roads are either blocked or mined.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:56.33,0:49:58.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且我們用信號塔和基地聯系了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}And since we used signal tower to talk to base,
Dialogue: 0,0:49:58.60,0:49:59.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所有人都知道我們的位置\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}everyone knows where we are.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:59.84,0:50:00.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們得盡快出去\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}We gotta move out.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:00.93,0:50:01.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些東西還在街上亂晃\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}So you wanna go running around out there
Dialogue: 0,0:50:01.92,0:50:04.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想在這種情況下出去嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}with those things roaming the streets?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:04.23,0:50:06.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們還沒有任何看到和對付它們的辦法\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Even though we have no way to see or fight?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:06.20,0:50:08.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總比等著它們闖進來要好\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Better than waiting for them to find a way in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:08.40,0:50:08.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪里好了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}How is it better?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:08.90,0:50:11.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們沒死的唯一原因就是外面的那道屏障\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}The only reason we're still alive is that barricade out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:11.60,0:50:12.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它們遲早會進來的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Look, eventually they're gonna get through.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:12.91,0:50:14.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是時間問題\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}It's just a matter of time.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:14.30,0:50:16.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-先消停一下  -我們得冒險一試\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- Wait, wait, wait. - We have to take our chances.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:16.83,0:50:18.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-這是目前最好的計劃  -少校\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- This is the best plan that we have. - Major.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:19.73,0:50:22.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我說我能增加成功到達廣場的幾率呢\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}What if I told you I can improve our chances of making that plaza?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:22.66,0:50:24.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-你說  -看看周圍\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- I'm listening. - Take a look around you.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:24.73,0:50:28.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這里到處都是這東西\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Everything in this building... is filled with these.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:29.73,0:50:30.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鐵屑\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Iron dust.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:32.26,0:50:34.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鐵能阻止那些超光譜異形\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}And the iron stops the hyperspectrals.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:34.66,0:50:36.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯  把它做成武器\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Exactly. Weaponize it.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:37.20,0:50:39.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-臟彈  -這是今晚最好的主意\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- Dirty bombs. - Best idea I've heard all night.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:40.13,0:50:41.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,收集手榴彈\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Let's collect the grenades.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:18.20,0:51:19.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克萊恩\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Clyne.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:19.76,0:51:21.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在外面我需要你做我們的眼睛\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I need you to be our eyes out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:21.60,0:51:23.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你能帶著攝像機走路嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Can you haul that camera on foot?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:23.52,0:51:24.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有更好的主意\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I've got a better idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:25.63,0:51:28.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個攝像機本身就能投射相符波長的紫外線\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}This camera already projects the right wavelength of UV light.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:29.33,0:51:30.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我能將它內部翻轉過來\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}If I can turn it inside out,
Dialogue: 0,0:51:30.71,0:51:33.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通過改變一些結構的極性\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}by reversing the polarity of some of the components,
Dialogue: 0,0:51:33.73,0:51:36.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也許能把攝像機改造成探照燈\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I might be able to turn it from a camera into a searchlight.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:37.06,0:51:39.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們憑肉眼就能看見它們\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}We'll be able to see them with our own eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:39.80,0:51:41.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這能大大改善我們的境況\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}That'd be a game-changer.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:41.25,0:51:42.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我能和基地的車隊通話嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Think I can talk to the convoy?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:42.90,0:51:44.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我或許能告訴它們\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I might be albe to tell them
Dialogue: 0,0:51:44.08,0:51:45.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如何對裝備做同樣的調整\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}how to do the same with their equipment.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:45.33,0:51:47.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們過來時也需要能看見它們的設備\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}When they come get us, they're gonna need eyes, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:48.30,0:51:50.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會幫你聯系基地的主工程師\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I'll connect you to the main engineer back at base.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:07.13,0:52:08.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,收到\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Copy that.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:10.03,0:52:12.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們會在車上裝備任何你需要的東西\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}They're ready to equip their vehicles with whatever you need.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:13.16,0:52:15.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能將需求列表復述一遍給我嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Can you repeat the whole request back to me, please?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:15.86,0:52:17.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對  沒錯\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Okay, yes. That's correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:17.60,0:52:18.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但你需要的是一個\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}But what you gonna need is a device
Dialogue: 0,0:52:18.82,0:52:20.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能發射短波長光的裝置\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}that emits a very short wavelength of light.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:21.03,0:52:23.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會詳細告訴你怎么改線\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I can tell you exactly how to rewire that.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:23.96,0:52:26.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么可以裝在坦克上的東西嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Do you have anything you can mount on a tank?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:16.90,0:53:18.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小巷那頭有動靜\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}We got movement across the alleyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:21.00,0:53:23.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伙計們  有動靜  能看看是什么嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Guys, we got movement. Can we get eyes on it?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:24.36,0:53:26.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻煩讓一下\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Hey, guys, stand clear for a second.
