Dialogue: 0,1:07:30.60,1:07:32.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們在民用的避難所\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}We're in a civilian refugee shelter.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:32.96,1:07:36.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這避難所有六米厚的鋼筋混凝土\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}This bunker has 20 feet of concrete and steel.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:36.06,1:07:38.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道在這里是否安全  但有食物和水\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Are we safe here? I have no idea. But there's food and water.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:39.00,1:07:40.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塔爾博特  盡可能收集物資\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Talbot, gather what you can.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:40.30,1:07:42.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,托爾  陳  回到入口處\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Toll, chen, head back to the entrance.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:42.13,1:07:44.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那里有通訊中心  看能聯絡到誰\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}There's a com center. See who you can reach.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:44.20,1:07:45.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿萊西奧  你和我一起  走吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Alessio, you're with me. Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:47.93,1:07:49.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-那邊  -哪里\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- There. - Where?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:49.26,1:07:50.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-那邊  -就在那里\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- There. - Right over there.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:50.83,1:07:51.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-好的  -放到床上\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- Okay. - On the bed.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:52.06,1:07:53.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事的  你會沒事的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You're okay. Shh. You're gonna be okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:55.30,1:07:57.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-怎么了  -是她的肩膀\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- What happened? - It's her shoulder.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:57.13,1:07:58.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-她的肩膀里有彈片\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- Her shoulder has shrapnel in it.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:58.70,1:08:00.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-我們要剪開衣袖\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- We're gonna cut open her sleeve.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:09.26,1:08:11.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,準備靜脈輸液管\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Get the IV line ready.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:14.93,1:08:15.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是你的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}This is yours.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:17.60,1:08:20.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莎莉  我現在需要你幫忙  為了阻止幽魂\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Now, I need your help, Sari, to stop the aratare.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:20.73,1:08:22.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我必須知道你爸爸所知道的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I need to know what your father knew.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:23.06,1:08:24.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你爸爸是做什么的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}What did your father do?
Dialogue: 0,1:08:25.60,1:08:28.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是制陶的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}He worked with ceramics.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:28.20,1:08:29.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他制作些什么呢\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}What did he make?
Dialogue: 0,1:08:33.76,1:08:35.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他制造容器\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}He made containers.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:39.66,1:08:41.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他為馬薩羅維制造容器\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}He made containers for Masarov.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:42.73,1:08:45.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幽魂就是來自那里的發電廠\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}The power plant where the aratare came from.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:47.03,1:08:48.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓她帶上氧氣面罩\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Let's get the mask on her.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:49.06,1:08:50.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在她得交給我們了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Okay, we have to take her now.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:01.76,1:09:04.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-我們是美國軍隊  -開門\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- This is the U.S. armed forces! - Open it.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:14.70,1:09:15.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放下武器\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Lower your weapons.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:34.63,1:09:36.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-你們有多少人  -不怎么多\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- How many are you? - Not many.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:51.13,1:09:52.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幫一下他們\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Let's give them a hand.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:53.96,1:09:54.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:56.13,1:09:57.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,盡可能多帶點\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Bring as much as you can.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:57.90,1:09:59.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基地被攻陷了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}The base was overrun.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:00.73,1:10:01.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那東西就像一道波浪\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}It was like a wave.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:03.06,1:10:04.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隱形的波浪\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Invisible.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:04.93,1:10:06.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家就開始倒下\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Men just started falling.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:07.60,1:10:09.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們的常規武器毫無作用\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Our conventional weapons were useless.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:10.60,1:10:12.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我請求下令撤離基地...\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I requested an order to evacuate the base...
Dialogue: 0,1:10:13.90,1:10:16.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但遠距離通訊系統完全被擾亂\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}But our long-range come are completely scrambled.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:17.13,1:10:18.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我把能帶的裝備都帶上\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}So, I took all the gear I could.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:18.96,1:10:22.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開始讓各小隊向北撤離行動區\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I started sending units north out of the area of operation.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:23.73,1:10:25.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓五架飛機保持最小耗燃量\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Kept five aircraft with the least amount of fuel,
Dialogue: 0,1:10:26.00,1:10:27.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟著一個排殿后\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}stayed behind with one platoon.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:31.06,1:10:33.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們240人只剩下19個了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Out of the 240 of us, we have 19 remaining.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:36.96,1:10:38.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有成功向上級通報嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Did you get a message to higher command?
Dialogue: 0,1:10:39.60,1:10:40.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}No.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:41.30,1:10:43.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有安排救援計劃嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Is there a rescue mission planned?
Dialogue: 0,1:10:43.01,1:10:44.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有  我們截取了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}No. We intercepted radio chatter
Dialogue: 0,1:10:44.70,1:10:46.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,摩爾多瓦友方無線電信號才找到這里\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}from Moldovan friendlies to find this place.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:46.86,1:10:49.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們派出直升機接你們過來\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}We sent that bird to pick you up and bring you here.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:49.80,1:10:52.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們要是試著回基地  就已經沒命了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}If you'd even tried to return to base, you'd be dead.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:54.23,1:10:56.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們是這個國家最后的美軍嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}We're the last U.S. Forces in the country?
Dialogue: 0,1:10:57.16,1:10:58.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但愿如此\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I hope so.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:00.33,1:11:01.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么計劃嗎  長官\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}So, what's the plan, sir?
Dialogue: 0,1:11:02.13,1:11:03.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來這里重新部署  少校\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Came here to regroup, Major.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:04.33,1:11:05.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什么計劃\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}There's no plan.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:11.76,1:11:14.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-我建議加固入口  -用什么加固\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- I recommend we fortify the entrance. - Fortify with what?
Dialogue: 0,1:11:14.86,1:11:17.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-我們等待救援...  -用什么加固\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- We wait till a rescue mission... - Fortify with what?
Dialogue: 0,1:11:17.76,1:11:19.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論你用什么東西  他們都能穿過\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}They'll come through whatever you use.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:19.73,1:11:21.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們得用直升機碰一碰運氣...\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}We need to take our chances get on one of our helos...
Dialogue: 0,1:11:21.81,1:11:23.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只能飛二十分鐘\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Twenty minutes of flight time!
Dialogue: 0,1:11:23.66,1:11:25.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直升機只剩二十分鐘的飛行時間了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}There's twenty minutes of flight time in those birds.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:25.56,1:11:26.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飛不了更久了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Not more!
Dialogue: 0,1:11:26.56,1:11:28.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關系  反正也裝不下所有人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Doesn't matter, there's not enough room for all of us...
Dialogue: 0,1:11:28.60,1:11:31.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們得組隊乘飛機\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}We need to form teams and take the aircraft.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:31.35,1:11:33.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但你要去哪里  少校\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}But where you gonna go, Major?
Dialogue: 0,1:11:34.28,1:11:35.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們躲不掉它們\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You can't run from them.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:36.30,1:11:39.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們無法阻止它們  你們的武器毫無作用\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You can't stop them. Your weapons are useless.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:40.60,1:11:42.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們不知道它們到底是什么\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}We have no idea what they are!
Dialogue: 0,1:11:42.76,1:11:45.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是它們穿門而入  我們只能坐以待斃\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}If they come through that door, we're sitting ducks.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:45.23,1:11:47.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們阻止不了它們  我們阻止不了它們\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}We can't stop them! We can't stop them!
Dialogue: 0,1:11:52.70,1:11:54.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把我們能帶走的都帶走\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Take what we can and go.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:57.83,1:11:58.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道它們是什么了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I know what they are.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:03.06,1:12:04.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道它們是什么了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I know what they are.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:05.96,1:12:07.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道它們是什么了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I know what they are.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:11.10,1:12:12.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們覺得我們見鬼了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}We think we're seeing things.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:13.13,1:12:15.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們覺得它不是真的  但它有殺傷力\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}We think it can't be real, but it kills.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:15.01,1:12:15.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以它是真的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}So, it is real.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:16.36,1:12:17.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是一種物質\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}It's something.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:17.90,1:12:19.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非光非影\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}It's not light, it's not shadow,
Dialogue: 0,1:12:19.49,1:12:21.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是幻覺  可以穿墻  沒錯\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}or some trick of the mind. Pass through walls, check.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:23.23,1:12:24.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,屬于非可見光譜  沒錯\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Outside the visible spectrum, check.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:26.33,1:12:27.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一觸即死  沒錯\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Kills to the touch, check.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:29.36,1:12:32.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,科姆斯托克當時躲在瓷浴缸底下  對吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Comstock. He was under a ceramic bathtub, is that right?
Dialogue: 0,1:12:34.13,1:12:36.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坦克裝甲  它不能穿過坦克裝甲\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Tank armor. It couldn't pass through tank armor.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:37.40,1:12:39.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,M1艾布蘭主戰坦克裝甲周身鍍瓷\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}M1 Abrams tank armor, that's ceramic plating everywhere.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:39.63,1:12:41.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它不能穿過瓷制品\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}It cannot pass through ceramic.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:41.64,1:12:42.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們知道這意味著什么嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You know what that means?
Dialogue: 0,1:12:43.10,1:12:45.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,意味著這東西不是天然的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}It means this stuff isn't natural.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:46.76,1:12:47.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人創造了它\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Someone made it.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:49.33,1:12:50.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它是人造的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}It's man-made.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:51.96,1:12:53.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么人造的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Man-made how?
Dialogue: 0,1:12:54.00,1:12:57.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世上有固體  液體  氣體\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Okay. You have solid, liquid, gas.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:57.85,1:12:58.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,熔巖可以凝固成巖石\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Lava can turn into rock.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:59.00,1:13:00.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冰可以融化成水\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Ice can turn into water.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:00.11,1:13:02.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,金屬能熔化  這些都是自然狀態\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Metals can melt. These are natural states.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:02.13,1:13:03.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但也有非自然狀態\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}But there are unnatural states.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:03.57,1:13:05.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人造狀態  人創造的狀態\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Artificial states, man-made states.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:06.76,1:13:07.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凝聚態\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Condensate.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:08.86,1:13:10.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玻色-愛因斯坦凝聚態\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Bose-Einstein condensate.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:10.76,1:13:11.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一種由奈斯·玻色\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}A state of matter that was
Dialogue: 0,1:13:11.96,1:13:13.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和阿爾伯特·愛因斯坦預測的一種物質狀態\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}predicted by Nath Bose and Albert Einstein.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:14.00,1:13:15.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它有一些非常反常的特性\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}It has some very unusual properties.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:15.86,1:13:17.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會被鐵屑減速\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}It can be slowed down by iron filings.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:17.90,1:13:21.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它不能穿過瓷制品  但卻可以穿墻\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}It cannot pass through ceramic, but it can pass through walls.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:21.10,1:13:23.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,溫度太低以致于一觸即死\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}It's so cold it will kill you instantly on contact.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:23.66,1:13:25.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它可以解釋我們所見的一切\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}It can do everything we've been seeing here.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:25.76,1:13:27.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要想產生波色-愛因斯坦凝聚態\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You want to create Bose-Einstein condensate.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:27.55,1:13:29.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們需要能量  大量的能量\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You need power, and you need a lot of it.
